<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śākābdē śaranāgasūryyagaṇitē vaiśākha śukla
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tṛtīyyāyāṁ sōmadinē śubhē naraharēssiṁhādribarttu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rmudā <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> snānārtthaṁ jalakuṁbhamēkamaniśaṁ prādātprasū
<lb n="4" break="no"/>nasrajaṁ śrīmān lakṣmaṇaśeṭṭivaryyatilaka<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> svābhīṣṭasaṁsi
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ddhayē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśaka<supplied reason="omitted">va</supplied>rṣaṁbulu 1285 gunēṁṭi vaiśākha śukla tṛ
<lb n="6" break="no"/>tiyyayu sōmavāramunāṁḍu munikulagotrōt bhūtuṁḍaina po
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṭṭanūri jiṣṇamaśeṭṭi koḍuku lakumanaśeṭṭi tanaku nabhīṣṭārtthasiddhi
<lb n="8" break="no"/>gānu śrīnarasiṁhyanāthuniki nityamunnu tirumajjana Avasaranaku
<lb n="9"/>jalakamu kuṁḍeṁḍu tēnu kuṁcaprasādamu ṭhāvuvaṭṭi māḍala narahariki
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṁ beṭṭenu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī tirumajjanamu tēnupeṭṭina tāṁbhagarayā Okaṭi <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> nityamu
<lb n="11" break="no"/>nnu dhuvakalānanu Oka tirumāla teccipeṭṭanu kuṁcaprasādamu ṭhāvuva
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ṭṭi bhūmi perumāṁḍi koḍuku parāIkiṁ beṭṭenu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Iṁttavaṭṭūnu
<lb n="13"/>[Ā]<supplied reason="omitted">caṁ</supplied>drārkkasrāhigānu cellaṁgaladu Ī dharmmu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrī
<lb n="14"/>śrī śrī
</p>

